To create a new level, you need to create 2 file.

A json file that specify the wave, order of ennemy, characher composing the
map

A map with only the character specified in the json file

filename.json
```json
{
    "map path": "./assets/data/game/level/map/map_1.txt",
    "squares path": {
        ".": "./assets/image/map/square/dirt.png",
        "N": "./assets/image/map/castle_with_nico.png",
        "o": "./assets/image/map/square/bush.png",
        "#": "./assets/image/map/square/path.png",
        "S": "./assets/image/map/square/path.png",
        "R": "./assets/image/map/square/rock.png",
        "T": "./assets/image/map/square/three.png"
    },
    "ennemy file": {
        "minion": "./assets/data/game/ennemy/minion.json",
        "fly": "./assets/data/game/ennemy/fly.json",
        "tank": "./assets/data/game/ennemy/tank.json",
        "kamikaze": "./assets/data/game/ennemy/kamikaze.json"
    },
    "com": 4,
    "wave": [["minion", 2, 0]],
    "tower nico life": 10
}
```

